                    <p>Your access to and use of the Service is conditioned on your acceptance of and compliance with these Terms. These Terms apply to all visitors, users, and others who access or use the Service.</p>

                    <p>By accessing or using the Service you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you disagree with any part of the terms, then you may not access the Service.</p>

                    <h2>1. Description of Service</h2>
                    <p>StromRadar provides informational widgets and interfaces displaying day-ahead electricity market prices, primarily sourced from public transparency platforms (such as ENTSO-E). The Service is intended to help users visualize energy market trends and estimate favorable times for electricity consumption.</p>

